<paragraph blockId="35.[189,355,642,668]" box="[189,355,642,668]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">
<heading bold="true" box="[189,355,642,668]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" reason="3">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,355,642,668]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Comparisons</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="35.[189,1399,688,785]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">
Closely related to 
<taxonomicName authority="Perrault, 1993" authorityName="Perrault" authorityYear="1993" box="[404,693,688,715]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Dyscolus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="moreti">
<emphasis box="[404,517,689,714]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">D. moreti</emphasis>
Perrault, 1993
</taxonomicName>
, but smaller (most specimens of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Perrault" authorityYear="1993" box="[1081,1194,689,714]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Dyscolus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="moreti">
<emphasis box="[1081,1194,689,714]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">D. moreti</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
range from 
<quantity metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.05" metricValueMax="1.1" metricValueMin="1.0" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" unit="mm" value="10.5" valueMax="11.0" valueMin="10.0">10 to 11 mm</quantity>
), the lateral margin of the pronotum narrower, the elytra narrower and less convex, the apex of the aedeagus shorter, more acute, and not bent ventrally as in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Perrault" authorityYear="1993" box="[912,1024,760,785]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Dyscolus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="moreti">
<emphasis box="[912,1024,760,785]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">D. moreti</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="35.[189,285,824,850]" box="[189,285,824,850]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">
<heading bold="true" box="[189,285,824,850]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" reason="3">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,285,824,850]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Habitat</emphasis>
